{"tid":1161134,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢d地方同性婚姻都係合法","createTime":"2019-05-19T03:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T11:47:14.000Z","uid":41355,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c73d46416d2fd6e52ea4bd1236099193c6a3c66","tid":1161134,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTSSuwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTSSuwE.jpg&h=59c954de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同性婚姻確保了同性配偶結合有權享有婚姻的權力同義務<br />\n<br />\n<strong>台灣同性／異性婚姻相同之處</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 年滿18歲的同性配偶可以登記結婚，婚姻當事人可收養另一方的「親生子女」，凖用民法「繼親收養」規定。<br />\n<br />\n2. 同性配偶擁有<span style=\"color: red;\">合法財產繼承權、醫療權</span>，但同時也必須遵守單一配偶相關權利義務。<br />\n<br />\n3. 同性伴侶一樣要<span style=\"color: red;\">受到婚姻規範包含通姦罪、重婚罪</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>台灣同性／異性婚姻不同之處</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 無法領養非親生子女。<br />\n<br />\n2. 目前<span style=\"color: red;\">只能與同婚通過的國家公民結婚</span>，大陸港澳伴侶也尚未納入專法。"},{"pid":"6248cd047a4db9a4c65ff7ed19841ab23f9a4230","tid":1161134,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"潮流興搞基，師兄幾時搞埋一份"},{"pid":"c5fe1cedd0c6ba9e8dc030d2f128acedb253e676","tid":1161134,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"#2 點解唔見左既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c382ef6ee7dc27aa38ea193a31e8f53fd3becae","tid":1161134,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48306662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48306662&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=1de7c695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48306662&h=cbe0e7be\" data-auto-link target=\